## Four Quadrants Explained:

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  RT (Research Theories) - Top Left                                      │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────      │
│  • Methodologically and empirically validated theories of CE            │
│  • Example: Notional machines validated through controlled experiments  │
│  • Evaluated by: Research methodology                                   │
│  • Contributes to: CE understanding                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  RD (Research Designs) - Bottom Left                                    │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  │
│  • Designs created with strict methodology for literature               │
│  • Example: Experimental curriculum design for theory testing           │
│  • Evaluated by: Research methodology                                   │
│  • Contributes to: CE practice (via research)                           │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  PT (Practice Theories) - Top Right                                     │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  │
│  • Useful theories/heuristics for practitioners                         │
│  • Example: "Students struggle with pointers" (observed, not validated) │
│  • Evaluated by: Usefulness in practice                                 │
│  • Contributes to: CE understanding (practitioner knowledge)            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  PD (Practice Designs) - Bottom Right                                   │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  │
│  • Designs created for impact, may/may not be evidence-based            │
│  • Example: Commercial educational tools, deployed curricula            │
│  • Evaluated by: Effectiveness in practice                              │
│  • Contributes to: CE practice                                          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


